headline: Ahead of Nordson (NDSN) Q4 Earnings: Get Ready With Wall Street Estimates for Key Metrics
summary: Beyond analysts' top -and-bottom-line estimates for Nordson (NDSN), evaluate projections for some of its key metrics to gain a better insight into how the business might have performed for the quarter ended October 2024.
